518
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:04,250
and a boss
to contend with.

519
00:18:04,333 --> 00:18:07,166
I overheard they’re a force
to be reckoned with.

520
00:18:09,083 --> 00:18:10,083
[DARK TIGER]
How fortuitous

521
00:18:10,166 --> 00:18:12,583
we have a shield of pawns.

522
00:18:17,916 --> 00:18:19,833
♪

523
00:18:21,041 --> 00:18:22,375
After this level
is cleared,

524
00:18:22,458 --> 00:18:24,500
the entrance to
Stage 0 should open up.

525
00:18:26,375 --> 00:18:27,625
[SUIGIN]
Hmm.

526
00:18:27,708 --> 00:18:29,041
At first glance,

527
00:18:29,125 --> 00:18:31,666
it doesn’t jump out at me
as being dangerous.

528
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,291
More importantly,
I need to figure out

529
00:18:33,375 --> 00:18:34,833
how I'm going to
locate Nishikaze

530
00:18:34,916 --> 00:18:36,375
among all these players.

531
00:18:36,458 --> 00:18:37,541
[gasps]

532
00:18:37,625 --> 00:18:38,875
It’s inconceivable this stage

533
00:18:38,958 --> 00:18:40,458
doesn’t have any guards!

534
00:18:40,541 --> 00:18:42,000
You guys should
go on ahead.

535
00:18:42,083 --> 00:18:44,041
I’ll just hang back and keep
an eye on things here.

536
00:18:45,458 --> 00:18:47,125
[yells]

537
00:18:47,208 --> 00:18:48,166
What’s wrong?

538
00:18:48,250 --> 00:18:49,166
[PLAYER 6 gasps]

539
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:51,208
[PLAYER 7]
Here they come!

540
00:18:51,291 --> 00:18:53,041
[PLAYER 8] I didn’t expect
the place to be crawling

541
00:18:53,125 --> 00:18:55,125
with this many tomb
beast guards!

542
00:18:55,208 --> 00:18:56,708
How come there are
so many enemies?

543
00:18:56,791 --> 00:18:58,000
I don’t know.

544
00:18:58,083 --> 00:18:59,416
But if the players
don’t work together,

545
00:18:59,500 --> 00:19:01,458
no one will
survive this battle.

546
00:19:01,541 --> 00:19:03,666
And it’s only
just begun.

547
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:06,791
♪

548
00:19:11,125 --> 00:19:13,291
What an interesting
assortment of items.

549
00:19:15,125 --> 00:19:17,125
[SUIGIN] I take it that’s
the portal to Stage 0.

550
00:19:18,416 --> 00:19:19,875
But who are those two?

551
00:19:19,958 --> 00:19:21,750
If I had to guess,
I’d say the one on the throne

552
00:19:21,833 --> 00:19:23,916
is Precious’s leader,
Dark Tiger.

553
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,916
[FARIN]
I didn’t think he’d be here!

554
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,625
[SUIGIN]
Dark Tiger.

555
00:19:27,708 --> 00:19:29,583
I keep running into
Billion Players.

556
00:19:31,333 --> 00:19:32,416
[DARK TIGER]
It won’t do us any good

557
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:33,958
to have our
meat shields wiped out

558
00:19:34,041 --> 00:19:35,041
by the first wave.

559
00:19:35,125 --> 00:19:36,375
Speed things up.

560
00:19:36,458 --> 00:19:39,250
Whatever you wish
shall be done, Dark Tiger.

561
00:19:39,333 --> 00:19:41,208
It’s time we
kick off the festivities

562
00:19:41,291 --> 00:19:42,833
in proper fashion!

563
00:19:42,916 --> 00:19:45,291
[BASHIDA]
Steel activate!

564
00:19:45,375 --> 00:19:47,208
Stallion Saber!

565
00:19:48,166 --> 00:19:50,416
[BASHIDA]
Centurion Buster!

566
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:52,833
Whoa. What the hell’s he doing?

567
00:19:52,916 --> 00:19:54,333
♪

568
00:19:58,083 --> 00:19:59,458
They defeated
all the monsters

569
00:19:59,541 --> 00:20:01,250
in a single blow.

570
00:20:01,333 --> 00:20:02,916
Is that Precious’s power?

571
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,125
It’s insane!

572
00:20:04,208 --> 00:20:05,333
[DARK TIGER]
Bashida.

573
00:20:05,416 --> 00:20:06,375
It’s time.

574
00:20:06,458 --> 00:20:07,375
Yes.

575
00:20:07,458 --> 00:20:08,541
Now that
the weaker elements

576
00:20:08,625 --> 00:20:09,666
have been dispatched,

577
00:20:09,750 --> 00:20:11,125
he should awaken
and the main event

578
00:20:11,208 --> 00:20:12,416
can finally begin.

579
00:20:15,625 --> 00:20:17,291
There’s no more
monsters to fight!

580
00:20:17,375 --> 00:20:19,375
[PLAYER 9] Which means only
the boss is left!

581
00:20:19,458 --> 00:20:21,583
And there’s enough of us
to clear the stage!

582
00:20:21,666 --> 00:20:22,750
No sweat!

583
00:20:25,833 --> 00:20:27,041
What, the?

584
00:20:27,125 --> 00:20:28,083
That isn't good!

585
00:20:28,166 --> 00:20:28,958
[PLAYER 10 screams]

586
00:20:29,041 --> 00:20:30,750
Why’s it that color?

587
00:20:30,833 --> 00:20:32,791
Uh, this isn’t
a pool of red water.

588
00:20:32,875 --> 00:20:34,208
It’s blood!

589
00:20:34,291 --> 00:20:35,583
-[PLAYER 11] Oh, god!
-[PLAYER 12] Watch out!

590
00:20:35,666 --> 00:20:37,083
[PLAYER 13]
Something’s forming out of it!

591
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:38,708
[PLAYER 14]
What the heck is that?

592
00:20:38,791 --> 00:20:39,791
I’m getting the feeling

593
00:20:39,875 --> 00:20:41,333
he’s not on our side.

594
00:20:41,416 --> 00:20:43,000
♪

595
00:20:43,083 --> 00:20:44,083
[FARIN]
Yeah.

596
00:20:44,166 --> 00:20:45,666
Stage 18’s boss.

597
00:20:45,750 --> 00:20:47,250
Aslan!

598
00:20:47,333 --> 00:20:48,333
[ASLAN]
Where is it?

599
00:20:48,416 --> 00:20:50,791
The blood I yearn
to gorge upon.

600
00:20:50,875 --> 00:20:52,083
[NISHIKAZE]
So jealous.

601
00:20:52,166 --> 00:20:53,666
Looks like a lot of fun.

602
00:20:53,750 --> 00:20:55,208
Think I’ll join them.

603
00:20:55,291 --> 00:20:56,791
[KITAKAZE]
You know our orders.

604
00:20:56,875 --> 00:20:59,125
Boss told us to wait here,
Nishikaze.

605
00:20:59,208 --> 00:21:01,458
Don’t do anything
you weren’t instructed.

606
00:21:01,541 --> 00:21:03,541
I don’t need
you to remind me.

607
00:21:03,625 --> 00:21:06,166
But you know how much
I detest waiting.

608
00:21:06,250 --> 00:21:07,958
I’ll go introduce myself.

609
00:21:08,041 --> 00:21:08,958
[ALL scream]

610
00:21:10,791 --> 00:21:13,125
Maximum power
and bring him down!

611
00:21:15,208 --> 00:21:16,583
Magic mirror, magic mirror,

612
00:21:16,666 --> 00:21:17,875
grant my wish.

613
00:21:17,958 --> 00:21:20,041
Tell me where the final
Tomb Guardian is.

614
00:21:20,125 --> 00:21:22,833
[PLAYER 15] Look!
The HP bar is replenishing!

615
00:21:22,916 --> 00:21:24,166
[PLAYER 16]
But he’s missing an arm!

616
00:21:24,250 --> 00:21:25,750
How can
it be filling up?

617
00:21:27,666 --> 00:21:28,791
That’s unreal.

618
00:21:28,875 --> 00:21:30,458
This boss can use
the pool of blood

619
00:21:30,541 --> 00:21:32,875
to regenerate
any damage he receives.

620
00:21:34,416 --> 00:21:35,708
Huh?

621
00:21:35,791 --> 00:21:38,125
[NISHIKAZE]
So you’re Suigin Riku?

622
00:21:38,208 --> 00:21:39,750
Ah!

623
00:21:39,833 --> 00:21:41,125
[SUIGIN screams]

624
00:21:43,166 --> 00:21:44,333
♪

625
00:23:43,500 --> 00:23:45,166
[SUIGIN]
The Silver Guardian!

